---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Comments from '../../components/Comments.astro';
---

<Layout title="强调语法 - Markdown 中文教程" description="学习在 Markdown 中创建粗体和斜体文本。">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="section section-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase text-[var(--color-terracotta)] mb-4">
            基础语法 / 强调
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-serif-display text-[var(--text-inverse)] mb-6">强调</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-[var(--text-on-dark)] opacity-80" style="line-height: 1.6;">
            通过将文本设置为粗体或斜体来强调其重要性。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>粗体（Bold）</h2>
          <p>要加粗文本，请在单词或短语的前后各添加两个星号（<code>**</code>）或下划线（<code>__</code>）：</p>

          <table class="w-full my-4">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-warm)]">
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">Markdown语法</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">预览效果</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>**bold text**</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><strong>bold text</strong></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>__bold text__</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><strong>bold text</strong></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h2>斜体（Italic）</h2>
          <p>要用斜体显示文本，请在单词或短语前后添加一个星号（<code>*</code>）或下划线（<code>_</code>）：</p>

          <table class="w-full my-4">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-warm)]">
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">Markdown语法</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">预览效果</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>*italic text*</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><em>italic text</em></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>_italic text_</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><em>italic text</em></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h2>粗体和斜体</h2>
          <p>要同时用粗体和斜体突出显示文本，请在单词或短语的前后各添加三个星号或下划线：</p>

          <table class="w-full my-4">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-warm)]">
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">Markdown语法</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium">预览效果</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>***bold and italic***</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><strong><em>bold and italic</em></strong></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-[var(--color-border-cream)]">
                <td class="py-2 px-3 font-mono text-sm"><code>___bold and italic___</code></td>
                <td class="py-2 px-3"><strong><em>bold and italic</em></strong></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Comments slug="basic-emphasis" />
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
